---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import site from '@/lib/site';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Anti-Aging &amp; Beauty IV Therapy | Menon Medispa | Millburn, NJ"
  description="Anti-aging and beauty IV drip therapy in Millburn NJ. Brighten skin, strengthen hair and nails, and fight signs of aging with our customized beauty infusions."
>
  <main class="sp" data-slug="anti-aging-beauty">

    <section class="sp-hero" aria-label="Anti-Aging &amp; Beauty IV Therapy in Millburn NJ">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-hero__grid">
          <div class="sp-hero__content">
            <h1 class="sp-hero__title">Anti-Aging &amp; Beauty IV Therapy in Millburn NJ</h1>
            <p class="sp-hero__eyebrow">Unlock a radiant glow and timeless beauty from within.</p>
            <p class="sp-hero__lead">Searching for the secret to glowing skin? True radiance starts on the inside. Our Anti-Aging &amp; Beauty IV drip in Millburn, NJ, is formulated to fight the signs of aging by detoxifying your body and promoting collagen production for a more youthful, vibrant appearance.</p>
            <div class="sp-hero__actions">
              <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Book Your IV Therapy</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-reviews">
              <div class="sp-reviews__avatars">
                <img src="/images/90411e0041df.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
                <img src="/images/305afeda5f9a.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
                <img src="/images/b95880091b44.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
              </div>
              <div class="sp-reviews__text">
                <span class="sp-reviews__stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span>
                <span class="sp-reviews__count">100+ 5 Star Reviews</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <img class="sp-hero__img" src="/images/1fb1073fea37.png" alt="Anti-Aging &amp; Beauty IV Therapy in Millburn NJ" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-badges" aria-label="Highlights">
      <div class="sp-container sp-badges__row">
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Brighten &amp; Hydrate Skin</p>
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Fight Signs of Aging</p>
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Strengthen Hair &amp; Nails</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-plain" aria-label="Formulas">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Choose Your Formula</h2>
          <div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">AGE-DEFYING Signature</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">Best for a targeted boost to achieve radiant skin and strengthen hair and nails.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">This potent formula delivers a concentrated blend of the most effective nutrients for detoxifying the skin, promoting a luminous glow, and building stronger hair and nails.</p>
            <ul style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0;"><li>Glutathione &amp; Vitamin C: A powerful antioxidant duo that detoxifies cells, fights free-radical damage, and helps create a bright, even skin tone.</li><li>Biotin &amp; Taurine: The essential building blocks for fortifying hair and nails, helping to reduce brittleness and promote healthy growth.</li><li>Minerals: Provides essential hydration, which is key to maintaining plump, youthful-looking skin.</li></ul>
          </div><div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">AGE-DEFYING Deluxe</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">Best for comprehensive rejuvenation, promoting collagen, reducing fine lines, and enhancing cellular repair.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">This all-in-one formula provides a full spectrum of vitamins, minerals, and amino acids to combat the signs of aging at a cellular level, supporting your body's natural repair and collagen production processes. Includes the core antioxidant &amp; Biotin foundation, plus:</p>
            <ul style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0;"><li>Complete B-Complex (B5, Niacin, etc.): A vital group of vitamins essential for cellular energy and repair.</li><li>Magnesium &amp; Zinc: Key minerals that help reduce skin inflammation and are crucial for collagen synthesis.</li><li>Amino Acids: The direct precursors to collagen and elastin, improving skin firmness and elasticity.</li></ul>
          </div>
          <p style="margin-top:2rem;"><a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Schedule Now</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-photos" aria-label="Customer Photos">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-photos__head"><h2>Hear From Our Customers!</h2></div>
        <div class="sp-photos__grid">
          <img src="/images/9ebaca3843d3.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/6c461885a28e.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/823792ea5ead.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/cd675890fe0d.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/2e5d1e68225a.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-plain sp-plain--alt" aria-label="Process">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Simple, Relaxing, and Effective</h2>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">01</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Personalized Consultation</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Your session begins with a brief consultation with one of our registered nurses. They will review your wellness goals and answer any questions to ensure your treatment is perfectly suited to your needs.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">02</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Relax and Recharge</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Once settled in our comfortable therapy lounge, the IV drip is administered. The process is virtually painless and takes about 45-60 minutes. You can relax, read, or catch up on emails while your body absorbs the nutrients.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">03</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Feel the Benefits</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Many clients report immediate benefits after their session. The nutrients continue to work for days, supporting your body's natural processes and helping you feel and look your best.</p></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-pricing" aria-label="Pricing">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-pricing__head">
          <h2>Book Your IV Therapy</h2>
          <p style="font-style:italic;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">All IV Drips are 500ml. Upgrade to 1000ml for only $25</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-pricelist">
          <div class="sp-priceitem">
            <img class="sp-priceitem__thumb" src="/images/f0e5c69d74a7.png" alt="AGE - DEFYING (Signature)" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="sp-priceitem__main">
              <a class="sp-priceitem__title" href="/booking-calendar/age-defying-signature">AGE - DEFYING (Signature)</a>
              <p class="sp-priceitem__sub">500ml.</p>
              <a class="sp-priceitem__readmore" href="/service-page/age-defying-signature">Read More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-priceitem__price">$200</div>
            <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold sp-priceitem__cta" href="/booking-calendar/age-defying-signature">Request to Book</a>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-priceitem">
            <img class="sp-priceitem__thumb" src="/images/f0e5c69d74a7.png" alt="AGE - DEFYING (Deluxe)" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="sp-priceitem__main">
              <a class="sp-priceitem__title" href="/booking-calendar/age-defying-deluxe">AGE - DEFYING (Deluxe)</a>
              <p class="sp-priceitem__sub">500ml.</p>
              <a class="sp-priceitem__readmore" href="/service-page/age-defying-deluxe">Read More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-priceitem__price">$250</div>
            <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold sp-priceitem__cta" href="/booking-calendar/age-defying-deluxe">Request to Book</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-testimonial" aria-label="What Our Clients Say">
      <img class="sp-testimonial__bg" src="/images/30cfb9e87c60.png" alt="" width="1440" height="626" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="sp-testimonial__overlay"></div>
      <div class="sp-container sp-testimonial__inner">
        <h2 class="sp-script-title sp-script-title--light" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">What Our <em>Clients</em> Say</h2>
        <blockquote class="sp-quote">
          <span class="sp-quote__mark">&ldquo;</span>
          Jennifer is amazing. Her aura and energy makes you feel welcomed and comfortable. Love our sessions! And my girl Rose Marie, the receptionist, is just lovely! I always leave with great joy after seeing them.
          <cite>Alexa C.</cite>
        </blockquote>
        <img src="/images/5be44787b3a9.png" alt="5 Star Google Reviews" width="143" height="74" loading="lazy" style="margin-top:1.75rem;" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-faq__card">
          <div class="sp-faq__head"><h2 class="sp-faq__title">Frequently asked questions</h2></div>
          <div class="sp-faq__list">
            <details class="sp-faq__item" open>
              <summary>What is Glutathione and why is it good for my skin?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>Glutathione is often called the body's "master antioxidant." Its primary role is to detoxify your cells and fight the free radical damage that causes aging. For your skin, this process can result in a brighter, more even complexion and reduce the appearance of blemishes.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>How is this IV drip better than topical creams or serums?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>Topical products work on the surface, while our Beauty IV Drip works from the inside out at a cellular level. By delivering nutrients with 100% absorption directly into your bloodstream, we nourish your skin, hair, and nails in a way that creams simply cannot.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>How long does it take to see results for my skin, hair, and nails?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>Many clients report an immediate "glow" and enhanced hydration right after their session. The more foundational benefits, such as improved skin elasticity and stronger hair and nails, build over time. Consistent treatments will yield the most noticeable and lasting results.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>How often should I get a Beauty IV drip to maintain results?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>For optimal results, we often recommend an initial series of drips followed by a maintenance plan. A typical maintenance schedule is one session every 2-4 weeks to continuously support collagen production and keep your skin looking luminous.</p></div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-cta" aria-label="Invest in Your Timeless Beauty">
      <div class="sp-container sp-cta__grid">
        <div class="sp-cta__copy">
          <h2 class="sp-cta__title">Invest in Your Timeless Beauty</h2>
          <p class="sp-cta__sub">Menon Medispa Millburn NJ</p>
          <p>Your journey to radiant skin, stronger hair, and lasting wellness starts here. Let our expert team help you choose the perfect IV therapy for your unique beauty goals.</p>
          <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-cta__media">
          <img src="/images/b1a819f35921.webp" alt="Menon Office Staff" width="431" height="560" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
